data.description: You will want to see this beautiful, open floor plan home in Hamilton, TX! It is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 4 car covered carport on .32 acres close to the beautiful downtown district. It sits on a corner lot with a big backyard including a nice covered back porch. Along with the open floor plan, it has wood  and tile floors throughout and a nice sized laundry room which includes a washer and dryer. The master is spacious with a large bathroom and roomy walk in closet. Make plans today to see this beauty in Hamilton!
